  ('promotion-8b44517b-moex-00007', 'promotion-8b44517b', 'promotion-8b44517b-moex-114-ad750edf', 'sub-promotion-8b44517b-02', NULL, 'essay', '根據我國現行工會法之規定，就有關於各直轄市、縣市行政主管機關所
